OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fdry evening with bright spells. Cloud
OL,7,Fwill thicken overnight with some
OL,8,Fpatchy rain spreading in from the west
OL,9,Fby the morning.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FA rather cloudy start with
OL,12,Fsome patchy light rain. Becoming dry
OL,13,Fwith some long spells of sunshine by
OL,14,Fthe afternoon. Another warm day.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FIt
OL,17,Fwill continue to be dry with long
OL,18,Fsunny spells. Feeling very warm but
OL,19,Fbecoming cooler along the east coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
